{"tid":338764,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)超人對蝙蝠俠 SABER係男人 奇異博士","createTime":"2017-07-28T12:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T19:02:22.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4461977611ee74fceb814b0f569dc3cc91dbeb","tid":338764,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:36:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=muqnOp0OfQeuf1dxuKqXozPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=187911e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK或者加V台個網入白名單好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=muqnOp0OfQeuf1dxuKqXozPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=8e465c7e\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=muqnOp0OfQeuf1dxuKqXozPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e37d47e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/13/Batman_v_Superman_poster.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F13%2FBatman_v_Superman_poster.jpeg&h=79d63a69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/83/King_Arthur_Legend_of_the_Sword_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F83%2FKing_Arthur_Legend_of_the_Sword_Poster.jpg&h=05238c61&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://geekget.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/%E5%A5%87%E7%95%B0%E5%8D%9A%E5%A3%AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgeekget.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2F%25E5%25A5%2587%25E7%2595%25B0%25E5%258D%259A%25E5%25A3%25AB.jpg&h=2f59bb76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.由超人和薩德將軍的恩怨所引發的「黑零事件」過了十八個月，超人成為了一個備受爭議的英雄人物，處於被支持者和反對者之間共同擠壓。與此同時，億萬富翁布魯斯&middot;韋恩已經化身為黑暗騎士「蝙蝠俠」，守護了高譚市接近二十年，而他因為在戰役中損失了位於大都會的韋恩集團分部與多名好友，開始將超人視為潛在威脅。而身為超人的克拉克&middot;肯特得知蝙蝠俠近年來的「暴力執法」<br />\n<br />\n2.亞瑟的父親烏瑟王在他年幼時即慘遭殺害，叔叔沃帝根(裘德洛 飾)篡奪了王位，亞瑟不僅被剝奪了王位繼承權，他甚至不知道自己的出身背景與皇家血統，失去父母的他獨自一人流落街頭，在弱肉強食的街頭中長大，也因此深刻體認了暴政下人民的痛苦..<br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述史蒂芬&middot;史傳奇（班奈狄克&middot;康柏拜區 飾）是一名世界頂級的神經外科醫生，生性驕傲、固執，直到一場車禍毀了他的工作能力；這使得他為了治療而去尋找「卡瑪泰姬」，進而遇見神秘的魔法師古一（蒂妲&middot;史雲頓 飾）。但當史傳奇在隨古一修練魔法的過程中，自己也陷入了古一和狂熱者們的爭鬥中。<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADB"},{"pid":"f78fd7801c51b5668af7147da870d5535fd544e7","tid":338764,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ebb10869801094268a2febe746492d52810645","tid":338764,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2a6f94fba7d7a4175b971954f021f66e8b18af","tid":338764,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75753f9a3e4bb07541347ff2f778cc476dacd01","tid":338764,"uid":29160,"lik